&lt;h1 id="is-light-a-particle-or-a-wave"&gt;Is Light a Particle or a Wave?&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apr 19 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;God does not play dice with the universe&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt; There&amp;rsquo;s a YouTube video in which Deutsch explains the famous quantum double-slit experiment, which is about particle-wave duality. Is light a particle or a wave? You pass it through a slit and, depending on whether there&amp;rsquo;s an observer and interference or not, it ends up in a wave pattern or as individual photons.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Probability Is Subjective</title><link>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/probability-is-subjective/</link><pubDate>Fri, 16 Apr 2021 17:31:04 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/probability-is-subjective/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/naval/zh/probability-is-subjective.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
